Source.Name: python-notebook
Source.Summary: A web-based notebook environment for interactive computing
Source.Description: The Jupyter Notebook is a web application that allows you to create and share documents that contain live code, equations, visualizations, and explanatory text. The Notebook has support for multiple programming languages, sharing, and interactive widgets.
